        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Initialized",
        "Ready",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以顶层是课堂服务的整体状态，Ready内部再展开ContentCDN的具体状态。那ContentCDN这边，Idle和Busy之间的切换是由什么触发的？还有出错之后怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Idle",
        "Busy",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN收到任务请求就从Idle转到Busy，任务完成回到Idle。如果任务执行失败，Busy要进入Error状态。Error里面再细分：先进入Retrying重试，重试成功返回Idle，重试次数超限则进入Failed。Failed之后可以通过reset操作回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Busy",
        "Error",
        "Retrying",
        "Failed",
        "task_received",
        "task_complete",
        "task_failed",
