      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Error是一个复合状态，内部包含Retrying和Failed。重试机制依赖学生数据库（StudentDB）来记录状态对吧？我看到命名里有Education_StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
