      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画好了：从ClassroomService开始，经过Initialized到Ready；Ready内部展开ContentCDN的Idle-Busy循环，Busy出错进入Error复合状态，Error里Retrying可以恢复或降级到Failed，Failed可reset。顶层Ready还能接收stop_signal进入Shutdown。请确认流转关系是否正确？",
      "elements_involved": [
